Company Charts

This vote was conducted to find out people's favourite Amiga company of
all time. We allowed people to vote for people like ClickBoom, Amiga
Inc and Vapoware because this was not, as some thought, a vote for
Amiga Retailers, it's a vote for Amiga companies. Here are the top
ten.

10 HiSoft
9  Blittersoft
8  Amiga Inc.
7  Power Computing
6  Weird Science
5  Newtek
4  Epic Marketing
3  Haage & Partner
2  Village Tronic
1  Phase 5

